data.description: Super cute and move in ready! Come see this 3 bedroom, 1 full bath ranch style home updated home! You will find beautiful hardwood floors in the living room, hallway and all bedrooms. Updated Kitchen with ss appliances (that stay), LVT flooring, custom built-in breakfast bar and plenty of cabinets! The laundry/utility room offer the washer/dryer (that stay), custom built-in storage pantry and additional cabinets. You'll love the updated bathroom with stone flooring, vanity/sink, shower panel and more! The master bedroom has created a large closet, bedroom 2 offers 2 closets and the smaller bedroom offers great natural light and endless possibilities! Newer updates include: roof, vinyl windows, central ac, h2o tank, external sump pump, kitchen, bath and more! The 1.5 car garage offers amazing storage shelving, workbench, electric and garage door opener! Off the garage is a covered patio to enjoy during nice weather! This home shows that is has been loved and cared for! Call for your private showing today! Seller requires preapproved buyers or those with proof of funds to view their property. All information believed to be accurate, but not guaranteed.
